# UI Architecture:
    ## Meta Approach:
        - (Persona, Channel, Use Case) approach
        - Channel Agnostic, Persona-focused Headless Access Services
        - Channel Adapters 
        - Web, Mobile, Email, MS Teams, as first-class channels
        - ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, etc., as first-class channels

    ## Hub Analytics Module:
        ✔ Report Center - Clarified as part of Hub Analytics using Olympus LakeStack @done(26-01-05)
        [ ] Product Center - Removed (not required)

    ## Hub Control Center (Tenant Admins):
        - Subsystems Configuration
            - Configuration: Task Management System
            - Configuration: API Gateway 
            - Configuration: Event Bus 
            - Configuration: File Gateway
            - Configuration: Automation Engines
            - Others

        - Tenant Ecosystem Setup
            - User and Access Management 
            - Machine Registry Management
            - Tool Registry Management
            - Workbench Management
            - Environments Management (?)

    ## Hub UI for Publisher:
        - Hub SRE Operations Center
        - Hub Win Operations Center
        
    ## Hub UI for Workbench Creators:
        - Hub Studio (Process Architects, Developers)
        - Hub Workbench - Steward Desk 

        Expand Workbench Studio:
            - Angelos Page (App) Builder (Custom Console Buildign use case)
            - Angelos Components and Binders (connects events from one component to tigger events in other components in a Page)
            - Angelos Action Repository
            - Scenario Builder (Signal -> Trigger -> Scenario -> Operation)
            - Automation Builder [Agentic] and Publisher [Agentic]
            - Knowledge Base Manager - SOPs, Reference Manuals, etc.,
            - Tool Registry (Subset of Tools applicable to this Workbench)
        
    ## Hub UI for Agents and Supervisors (Per Workbench):
        - Hub Workbench - Agent Desk
        - Hub Workbench - Supervisor Desk (Manage and Govern)
        - Hub Home (Landing page for Agents and Supervisors; Provides list of workbenches, tasks, agents, etc., Quick Access to common tasks, Alerts and Notifications)

        Expand Agent Desk:
            - Consoles (Utility Consoles, Custom Consoles)
            - Task Solver Interface (Custom for each task type; Can be defined by the Workbench Developer; Provide read-only and solver-views for the task)
        
        Expand Utility Consoles (Common to Agent Desk and Supervisor Desk) :
            - Tasks
            - Files
            - Reports
            - Knowledge Base
            - Signals (Exceptions, Observations, and Others)
            - Routines & Checklists
            - Analytics (Supervisor Desk)
            - Task Allocation Management (Supervisor Desk)
            - Agents & Access Management (Supervisor Desk)
        
    ## MCP Architecture:
        - MCP Router (infrastructure)
        - MCP Channels (persona-scoped):
            - Tenant Admin MCP Channel
            - Creator MCP Channel       
            - Agent MCP Channel 
            - Supervisor MCP Channel
            - Business User MCP Channel (Dataplane):
                - Service Request
                - Business Request
                - System Request
    ## Business Customer aka Service Request Interfaces:
        - Use of Neutrino Channels for Business Customer
        - Task Solver Components for Subject Tasks
        - Integration into Neutrino Channels - Mobile, Web, Email, MS Teams, etc.,

